org.jdrupes.json

Interface JsonArray

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonArray.DefaultJsonArray, JsonArray.JsonArrayWrapper

    public interface JsonArray

    A view on a List<Object> that provides some utility methods for accessing the data.
